query:
INSERT INTO printed_ballots (
            id,
            client_id,
            machine_id,
            common_access_card_id,
            common_access_card_certificate,
            registration_id,
            cast_vote_record,
            cast_vote_record_signature
        )
        VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4, $5,
            (SELECT id FROM registrations WHERE client_id = $6),
            $7, $8
        )
